Devana
Devana is a company based in Herbignac, specializing in generative AI technology since 2019. They provide a unique platform and embedded technologies that ensure the reliability and traceability of generated information, positioning themselves as high-performance aggregators of multimodal generative artificial intelligences. Their centralized and secure environment, 'the HUB', makes generative AI models accessible with an intuitive interface and pre-trained models, democratizing AI usage.

Herbignac
Herbignac is the location where the company Devana is based, indicating its geographical presence.

Generative AI
Generative AI refers to a type of artificial intelligence technology that Devana specializes in, enhancing information reliability and traceability.<SEP>Generative AI refers to the branch of artificial intelligence focused on creating content or performing tasks autonomously. Lumiere Formation offers training in its application.

The HUB
The HUB is a centralized and secure environment developed by Devana, designed to allow users to easily and dynamically use generative AI models.

Multimodal Generative Artificial Intelligences
Multimodal Generative Artificial Intelligences are diverse AI models that Devana aggregates with high performance, enabling varied applications across multiple modalities.

Intuitive Interface
The Intuitive Interface is part of Devana's HUB, designed to simplify the use of generative AI for users without data science or programming expertise.

Pre-trained Models
Pre-trained Models are part of Devana's offering, facilitating easy access to advanced generative AI capabilities for users.

Polaria
Polaria is a company based in Finistère, operating throughout France. It focuses on GenAI activities, including conferences, training, and development of bespoke solutions. Through its technological subsidiary, it develops chatbot and conversational AI solutions, including generative AI since 2016. Its mission includes contributing to French, European, and Open Source AI technologies, and facilitating human, organizational, and managerial transformations related to AI.

Finistère
Finistère is a geographic location where Polaria's headquarters are situated and from where it operates its activities across France.

Conferences on Acculturation
Polaria holds conferences focused on acculturation, providing insights into AI technologies and their integration.

data.entity_name: Development of Chatbot and Conversational AI
data.content:
Development of Chatbot and Conversational AI
Polaria's technological subsidiary is involved in developing chatbot and conversational AI solutions, including generative AI since 2016, aimed at creating advanced communication technologies.

Training and Bespoke Solutions Development
Polaria offers training services and develops tailor-made AI solutions to meet specific client needs, emphasizing human-centered, AI-guided strategies.

Technological Subsidiary
Technological Subsidiary is a part of Polaria responsible for developing chatbot and conversational AI solutions, including generative AI.

French AI Technologies
Polaria contributes to the development of conversational and generative AI technologies in France, emphasizing local innovation and advancement.

European AI Technologies
Polaria is involved in the development of conversational and generative AI technologies across Europe, focusing on collaborative and innovative solutions.

Open Source AI Technologies
Polaria participates in the development of open-source conversational and generative AI technologies, promoting shared growth and innovation.

Human, Organizational, and Managerial Transformations
Polaria aids in the transformations driven by AI in human, organizational, and managerial contexts, helping entities adapt to new technological landscapes.

Human-Centered, AI-Guided Strategies
Polaria guides organizations in developing strategies that are both human-centered and AI-guided, ensuring balanced technological integration.

Qwanteos
Qwanteos is a company that provides a comprehensive data processing service for AI professionals, focusing on precise and exhaustive annotation and labeling of data sets to ensure the optimal functioning of AI models.

Nantes
Nantes is the geographic location where Kalent is based.<SEP>Nantes is the location where the company Qwanteos is based.

GenAI
GenAI refers to a category encompassing generative AI technologies, under which Angel Start's AI coach operates to aid business planning.<SEP>GenAI refers to generative artificial intelligence, a technology used to enhance productivity and creativity through AI-generated content.<SEP>GenAI refers to the activities related to generative artificial intelligence, involving data processing and model optimization.<SEP>GenAI refers to the category of AI technologies that Miakito focuses on in its activities, such as training, audits, diagnostics, and solution development.<SEP>GenAI refers to the category of AI technologies focused on providing advanced, generative solutions across various fields, including music.<SEP>GenAI refers to the category of generative artificial intelligence technologies that Kalent employs to optimize recruitment processes.<SEP>GenAI refers to the use of artificial intelligence technologies to optimize content for social media.

Data Processing
Data Processing includes the annotation and labeling of datasets, crucial for the functioning of AI models, as offered by Qwanteos.

Miakito
Miakito is a company that develops custom AI solutions to automate repetitive tasks. Their activities include training, audits, diagnostics, and solution design.

Rennes
Rennes is the city where Backprop is based, situated in Brittany, France.<SEP>Rennes is the geographic location where Miakito is based.<SEP>Rennes is the geographical location where Airon Band is based.<SEP>Rennes is the geographical location where 2050score is based.<SEP>Rennes is the geographic location where Feelim is based, indicating it as their main operational area.<SEP>Rennes is the geographic location where Lumiere Formation is based, indicating its place of operation and central hub.<SEP>Rennes is the geographic location where Conjecto is based.

Airon Band
Airon Band is a company based in Rennes that provides AI-powered career management solutions for independent artists and music professionals, helping to optimize visibility, monetization, and administrative task management.

AI
AI refers to artificial intelligence, utilized by Airon Band to enhance career management solutions for artists and music professionals.

Artistes Indépendants
Artistes Indépendants refers to independent artists who form part of the primary clientele for Airon Band's AI-powered career management platform.

Professionnels de la Musique
Professionnels de la Musique are music professionals who benefit from Airon Band's AI-driven solutions for optimizing visibility, monetization, and administrative management.

Backprop
Backprop is a company based in Rennes, providing training and consultancy in generative AI to Breton businesses. They help SMEs integrate AI to boost productivity and creativity.

Breton businesses
Breton businesses are companies located in the Brittany region of France that potentially benefit from Backprop's services in generative AI.

SMEs
SMEs (Small and Medium-sized Enterprises) are businesses that Backprop aids by integrating AI to enhance their productivity and creativity.

Angel Start
Angel Start is a company that has developed an AI coach to assist project leaders in structuring their ideas and generating forecasts, aligning with business plan facilitation through AI technology.

Saint-Malo
Saint-Malo is the geographical location where Angel Start is based, providing a physical presence for the organization.

big bpi
Big BPI is an event where Angel Start plans to present their AI technology, suggesting their proactive engagement with industry showcases.

IA Coach
IA Coach is the AI-based tool developed by Angel Start to assist project leaders in structuring their ideas and generating business forecasts.

2050score
2050score is a company that collects, structures, evaluates, and shares public information from all EU enterprises regarding their progress towards a desirable economy by 2050. The company focuses on the key challenges of the Green Deal including carbon neutrality, circular economy, biodiversity protection, sustainable finance, social justice, and transparent governance.

Green Deal
The Green Deal refers to the EU's comprehensive plan to make the economy sustainable by addressing issues such as carbon neutrality, circular economy, biodiversity protection, sustainable finance, social justice, and transparent governance.

Carbon Neutrality
Carbon Neutrality is a state of net-zero carbon dioxide emissions, achieved through balancing emissions with removal efforts, which is part of the Green Deal challenges addressed by 2050score.

Circular Economy
Circular Economy is an economic system aimed at eliminating waste and the continual use of resources, part of the Green Deal focus areas for 2050score.

Biodiversity Protection
Biodiversity Protection involves conserving species, habitats, and ecosystems, which is a major goal of the Green Deal and a focus for 2050score.

Sustainable Finance
Sustainable Finance refers to financial services integrating environmental, social, and governance (ESG) criteria, aligned with 2050score's objectives under the Green Deal.

Social Justice
Social Justice is about equitable distribution of resources and opportunities, a societal goal aligned with the Green Deal, which 2050score aims to support.

Transparent Governance
Transparent Governance involves decision-making processes that are open and accountable, part of the Green Deal principles supported by 2050score.

Kalent
Kalent is a recruitment platform powered by artificial intelligence, dedicated to helping companies find and engage qualified talent quickly. It offers a vast database of 25 million profiles with updated contact information and full GDPR compliance. The platform provides AI-driven search filters, personalized recruitment campaigns, and integration with ATS systems.

Recruiters
Recruiters are users of the Kalent platform who use AI filters to refine their search for qualified candidates quickly.

ATS (Applicant Tracking System)
ATS refers to software systems that companies use to handle their recruitment processes, which can be integrated with Kalent for automation.

LinkedIn
LinkedIn is a professional networking platform used by Kalent for multi-channel recruitment campaigns.

WhatsApp
WhatsApp is a messaging application used by Kalent to conduct multi-channel recruitment outreach.

Email
Email is a communication method used by Kalent for conducting personalized recruitment campaigns.

Feelim
Feelim is a company that helps optimize content for social media using artificial intelligence (GenAI).

Social Media
Social Media platforms where content is optimized using Feelim's AI technology, enhancing reach and engagement.

Lumiere Formation
Lumiere Formation is a company based in Rennes, specializing in training organizations such as enterprises, unions, and media outlets on the use of Generative AI. They offer a flagship one-day workshop focused on practical exercises.

Enterprises
Enterprises are one of the categories of organizations that Lumiere Formation provides Generative AI training for, helping them integrate AI into their operations.

Unions
Unions are another category of organizations that receive Generative AI training from Lumiere Formation, aiming to enhance their understanding and application of AI technologies.

Media Outlets
Media Outlets are included in the range of organizations that Lumiere Formation assists, focusing on how these outlets can benefit from Generative AI solutions.

Conjecto
Conjecto is a company involved in training, consulting, and developing solutions related to Generative AI.

Chaire Managia
Chaire Managia is an organization aiming to explore the impact of conversational and generative artificial intelligence on management practices. It is co-founded by the Polaria Group, ISEN Ouest engineering school, and the Strate School of Design.

Polaria Group
Polaria Group is one of the co-founders of Chaire Managia, involved in exploring AI impact on management.

ISEN Ouest
ISEN Ouest is an engineering school co-founding Chaire Managia, focusing on AI impact.

Strate School of Design
Strate School of Design is a design school co-founding Chaire Managia, focusing on AI impact.

Brest
Brest is the location where Chaire Managia is based.<SEP>Brest is the location where Tristan Legros is based.

Intelligence Artificielle Conversationnelle
Intelligence Artificielle Conversationnelle refers to conversational artificial intelligence, which is a focus area in Chaire Managia's mission to explore its impact on management.

Intelligence Artificielle Générative
Intelligence Artificielle Générative refers to generative artificial intelligence, which Chaire Managia is researching for its potential impact on management practices.

Tristan Legros
Tristan Legros is a freelance creative consultant and trainer specializing in tools for creating images and videos. He works frequently with agencies and clients such as Publicis, Coty, Renault, and Mondelez.

Publicis
Publicis is an agency with which Tristan Legros frequently collaborates.

Coty
Coty is a client of Tristan Legros, indicating a business relationship.

Renault
Renault is a client of Tristan Legros, indicating a business relationship.

Mondelez
Mondelez is a client of Tristan Legros, indicating a business relationship.

Creation Tools
Creation Tools include a variety of software and platforms used by Tristan Legros to create images and videos, such as Midjourney, Seelab.ai, EverArt, Adobe Firefly, Flair.ai, Runway, Pika, and Kling.

Midjourney
Midjourney is a platform or tool used by Tristan Legros for generating creative content.

Seelab.ai
Seelab.ai is a tool utilized by Tristan Legros to support his creative consultancy work.

EverArt
EverArt is a creative tool employed by Tristan Legros in his consultancy and training activities.

Adobe Firefly
Adobe Firefly is a platform used by Tristan Legros for creative tasks involving images and videos.

Flair.ai
Flair.ai is a tool that Tristan Legros uses as part of his creative consultancy toolkit.

Runway
Runway is one of the many creative tools used by Tristan Legros to fulfill client requirements.

Pika
Pika is included in the suite of creative tools used by Tristan Legros for generating images and videos.

Kling
Kling is a creative tool utilized by Tristan Legros to support his freelance activities.
